records.name: Sun Siyam Iru Fushi With Free Transfer

descriptions.direction: Located in Iru Fushi, Sun Siyam Iru Fushi is on the beach. While the natural beauty of Velaa Private Island and Kuredu Beach can be enjoyed by anyone, those looking for an activity can check out Orimasvaru Island Pier. Looking to get your feet wet? Snorkeling and swimming adventures can be found near the property.
descriptions.general: Indulge in a rejuvenating experience at the spa, offering massages, body treatments, and facials. For recreation, you'll find a health club, outdoor pool, and waterslide. This resort also provides complimentary Wi-Fi, concierge services, and babysitting (surcharge). All-inclusive rates are available, covering meals and beverages at onsite dining establishments. Charges may apply for select restaurants, special dinners, dishes, beverages, and other amenities. Savor Asian cuisine at BAMBOO, one of the resort's 10 restaurants, or enjoy 24-hour room service. Unwind with a drink at one of the 5 bars/lounges. The resort features express check-in/check-out, complimentary newspapers in the lobby, a conference center, and 8 meeting rooms. Airport shuttle service is available (surcharge). Each of the 221 air-conditioned rooms offers a minibar, flat-screen TV with satellite programming, complimentary Wi-Fi, and a private bathroom with a shower, complimentary toiletries, and a bidet. A safe, desk, and phone with free international calls are also provided. Distances are calculated in a straight line from the property's location and may not reflect actual travel distance. Nearby points of interest include Randheli Arrival Jetty (6 km), Grand Friday Mosque (10 km), and Velaa Private Island (16 km).
